<HTML><HEAD> <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/style.css"><Title>Jacques Maritain Center: GC 3.20a</title></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#EEEEEE">><A HREF="gc.htm"> Of God and His Creatures</a><hr>

<p>Still the essence is limited, and the actual being accordingly 
finite and created.  He refers of course to the angels, who are 
'pure forms' (B. II, Chap. L).</p>

<hr>

